msg: merge with the latest trunk head.
Refactored PageMap a bit (by far perfect.. :( ) but now we can have simple pagemaps
The SecondLevelPageMap caches only the last used page (first level).
If that doesn't hit then the softcache is asked (second level)
If that also doesn't hit then the perminant store is asked, currently
one implementation: FileStore that stores the pages to the work dir of the container.
